{"title":"人民的好战士","authors":["韩笑"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":7,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的好战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韩笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南海蛟龙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——赞王国权同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁相信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这“南海蛟龙”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还不会游泳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海对着他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张牙舞爪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像戏弄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守岛的新兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排长指着那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天边的鬼影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无声的命令！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他想起父亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为阶级的解放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是怎样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英勇牺牲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血腥的屠刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在面前！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他跳起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向狂澜猛冲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁愿喝几口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦咸的海水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绝不能再喝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辛酸的眼泪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他在烈日下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"练一身"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢骨铁胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让白鷗赞叹；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他在怒涛中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挎钢枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万米长征，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让鲨鱼吃惊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄严的五指山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欣慰地招手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像呼唤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打天下的好汉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄的后代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能战胜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨浪狂风！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色的接班人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——赞刘瑞明同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫笑他军衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"补丁如花瓣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比鲜花迷人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比奖章耀眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里面藏着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忠心和赤胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香风攻不透，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毒箭射不穿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮丽的理想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在汗珠上发光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为阶级的事业"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他起早贪晚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百宝箱提在手上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"针线包带在身边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作连队的管家人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他手脚不停闲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崇高的志愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在火炮里闪闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听党的教导"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他勤学苦练。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牢记地狱的皮鞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向往天堂的花园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当人民的好战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在风浪中向前！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他惋惜蝴蝶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辜负了春光灿烂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他赞美蜜蜂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也懂得忆苦思甜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在他面前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能不深思："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色的接班人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从哪里接班！？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（宗怡插图）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}